ast, present and future, no matter whether I have suffered from illness, political persecution, hardship or any other situation, I will never commit suicide. I have no enemies other than tyranny. If I suffer from accidents, suicides, disappearances or any unnatural deaths, including accidents such as car accidents and drowning, they are all murdered by the CCP and the Hong Kong Communist Government. <br />\n<br />\n#我不自殺聲明<br />\n#NoSuicideStatement<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>麻煩大家係FB/IG tag3個朋友再share出去！麻煩文宣整個我不自殺logo畀人轉FB/ IG icon!!!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">831 失蹤左幾多個？新屋嶺拉左幾多個？放左幾多個？</span><br />\n<br />\n上個post<br />\n建議發起我不自殺聲明運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548031\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548031</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5e5d12d66177ff83189ead366354343aa05c42be","tid":1548844,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:10:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又就嚟到四點</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0117a140730c88ac11d152d00606ec97fb400d94","tid":1548844,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50dc1318fdb92e3544ed7194cc73dcd9a83c5669","tid":1548844,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:12:25.000Z","msg":"順撚到扑街<br />\n利申 車手"},{"pid":"c4f9a626a19fd05db0b92a700cd8cb9deab547ee","tid":1548844,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:12:40.000Z","msg":"室外位置真係狗多過人 , 狗係包括埋機場保安同執達史"},{"pid":"4